1
00:00:57,982 --> 00:01:00,958
=Within The Grip=

2
00:01:00,958 --> 00:01:02,928
=Episode 16=

3
00:01:02,928 --> 00:01:06,950
(Freedom)

4
00:01:07,040 --> 00:01:09,864
(Vast Mind, Eternal Will)

5
00:01:21,239 --> 00:01:23,159
What happened? Where's Yuluo?

6
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:26,079
Taken away by Master Chaosheng's man.
He doesn't mean well.

7
00:01:26,319 --> 00:01:28,359
It might be related to Master Zhaoxi.

8
00:01:38,319 --> 00:01:40,519
Do you recognize what this is?

9
00:01:42,519 --> 00:01:44,439
If Gu Zhaoxi's remains aren't in here,

10
00:01:46,159 --> 00:01:48,359
why steal it away and secretly bury it?

11
00:01:49,480 --> 00:01:50,879
If Gu Zhaoxi is dead,

12
00:01:51,719 --> 00:01:53,280
who is that one in the Fufeng Pavilion?

13
00:01:53,879 --> 00:01:55,640
You schemed tirelessly
to enter our family.

14
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:58,000
All for the position
of Xuanji Pavilion Master.

15
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:05,159
Pity that although the Pavilion
controls intelligence networks,

16
00:02:05,879 --> 00:02:07,480
it remains subordinate to our family.

17
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:10,759
Setting aside whether you're involved
in Gu Zhaoxi's death,

18
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:13,960
if Father ever learns of this,

19
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:17,080
do you think he'll spare you?

20
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:20,199
What do you expect of me?

21
00:02:22,199 --> 00:02:23,800
Seems you know your place.

22
00:02:24,639 --> 00:02:27,280
I expected more trouble from you.

23
00:02:28,879 --> 00:02:29,680
Fine.

24
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,599
Let's speak plainly.

25
00:02:31,879 --> 00:02:33,960
If you want the Xuanji Pavilion, fine.

26
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:36,639
But you must submit to me

27
00:02:37,479 --> 00:02:39,360
and help me become the Gu family head.

28
00:02:39,759 --> 00:02:42,879
Otherwise, the Pavilion Master
could be you

29
00:02:43,719 --> 00:02:45,080
or someone else.

30
00:02:47,919 --> 00:02:48,960
What's so funny?

31
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:51,240
Master Zhaoxi, you cannot enter!

32
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:58,159
I'm just curious.

33
00:02:59,199 --> 00:03:03,159
Why are you hastily staging
this treacherous scheme?

34
00:03:03,719 --> 00:03:05,120
Are you backing out now?

35
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,599
Now, I have the evidence.

36
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:10,680
Whether I give these bones
to the yamen or Father...

37
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:11,680
The bones?

38
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:15,039
Do you truly believe
this box contains bones?

39
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:26,879
My husband is right here.

40
00:03:27,319 --> 00:03:29,520
Have those rumors
made you unable to recognize

41
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:30,800
your own brother?

42
00:03:31,159 --> 00:03:32,560
I also visited the temple today.

43
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:36,280
Officials found this pouch,
and I found it familiar.

44
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,960
Then I remembered it.

45
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:41,599
So I had Xuan Qing steal it away,

46
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:44,319
planning to handle it later

47
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:46,800
to prevent the yamen
from suspecting you.

48
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:50,479
You buried a mere pouch in a wooden box?

49
00:03:50,599 --> 00:03:52,719
Do you truly think
others don't see your scheme?

50
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:04,599
I heard you went to Gu Xuanwu
after the family head refused you.

51
00:04:04,759 --> 00:04:06,719
He lent you these men.

52
00:04:07,719 --> 00:04:10,800
But if he refused
to help with the pouch,

53
00:04:11,199 --> 00:04:14,520
why would he lend you men to coerce me?

54
00:04:15,319 --> 00:04:16,920
You didn't kill that person.

55
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:19,920
Why fear the yamen's investigation?

56
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:22,399
As for my intentions,

57
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:25,759
a corpse found
at the temple points to you.

58
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:29,120
As part of the Gu family,
I want to clean up your mess.

59
00:04:29,759 --> 00:04:33,519
But I must uncover the truth

60
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:39,240
and determine if you deserve my help.

61
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:40,879
You...

62
00:04:41,319 --> 00:04:43,279
Since I could steal the pouch,

63
00:04:43,439 --> 00:04:46,600
I'll uncover every detail of this.

64
00:04:47,279 --> 00:04:51,759
But the power is in my hands now.
Your choice decides all.

65
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:31,199
May our future cooperation be smooth.

66
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:33,120
Look at the state of this family.

67
00:05:33,439 --> 00:05:35,639
Have you noticed nothing?

68
00:05:36,079 --> 00:05:39,639
You hired Leng Yan and killed Wanniang
through the Xuanji Pavilion.

69
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:42,040
You really think
no word of that got out?

70
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:47,160
You used a physician to test
if Zhaoxi remembered that jade pendant.

71
00:05:48,279 --> 00:05:51,519
But how could you be sure
he was an ordinary physician?

72
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:15,439
At this point, do you still see
all these things as mere family affairs?

73
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:22,920
Might as well recall what drove you
to hire an assassin

74
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:29,079
and to bring Physician Li
to examine Zhaoxi.

75
00:06:29,079 --> 00:06:30,240
I never hired any assassin.

76
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:32,879
Physician Li only came
for Zhaoxi's health.

77
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:34,839
Easy.

78
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:37,319
Take your time to think about it.

79
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:39,279
It's getting late now.

80
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:42,279
I'll leave it to you
to deal with these corpses.

81
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:44,279
But,

82
00:06:45,399 --> 00:06:48,360
may you still sleep soundly tonight.

83
00:06:54,279 --> 00:06:56,639
I don't know
what Gu Xuanwu promised you.

84
00:06:57,120 --> 00:07:00,879
But you'd better steer clear of him.

85
00:07:25,199 --> 00:07:25,759
Dear.

86
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:30,240
The guards reported nothing.
Will Chaosheng be in danger?

87
00:07:30,639 --> 00:07:31,279
Danger?

88
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:34,879
Wouldn't luring out
the mastermind be better?

89
00:07:38,079 --> 00:07:39,319
You really want to get into

90
00:07:40,279 --> 00:07:41,279
the Physician Qin matter?

91
00:07:41,959 --> 00:07:43,800
I hadn't planned to.

92
00:07:44,879 --> 00:07:46,439
But didn't you say

93
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:50,040
instead of waiting
to judge others' intentions,

94
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,720
we should leave them a path to goodness?

95
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:59,680
With you so compassionate,

96
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:02,279
how could I recklessly take a life?

97
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:27,240
You should know this isn't compassion.

98
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:29,399
In this world of power,

99
00:08:30,279 --> 00:08:31,399
instead of killing someone,

100
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:35,039
why not turn them
into a blade in your hands?

101
00:08:35,639 --> 00:08:37,120
It's clear the latter benefits more.

102
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,000
But...

103
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:42,200
I'm nothing but a blade
in someone else's hands.

104
00:08:47,159 --> 00:08:50,480
Then why did you get
yourself into this mess?

105
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:53,159
Why trap yourself here?

106
00:08:53,879 --> 00:08:56,879
Is all of this truly what you want?

107
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:02,399
What do you think I want?

108
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:08,639
Freedom.

109
00:09:12,639 --> 00:09:13,440
Freedom.

110
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,080
What do you think

111
00:09:18,799 --> 00:09:19,919
is freedom?

112
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:37,440
Soaring birds are free.

113
00:09:38,039 --> 00:09:39,639
Swimming fish in the sea are free.

114
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:44,279
But there are bows
and nets in the world,

115
00:09:44,639 --> 00:09:48,480
so the freedom we see
before us is only fleeting smoke.

116
00:09:48,919 --> 00:09:50,320
The mundane world is a cage.

117
00:09:51,679 --> 00:09:52,759
In my opinion,

118
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:59,559
true freedom is having a blade in hand.

119
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:03,240
Why didn't you let
Xuan Qing come with you?

120
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:06,840
She has more important things to do.

121
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:08,559
Is that so?

122
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:11,840
Or is it because you never trust anyone?

123
00:10:12,799 --> 00:10:14,240
But I'm very happy

124
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,080
that you came today.

125
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:22,080
It's getting late.

126
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:23,240
Let's go.

127
00:10:33,824 --> 00:10:36,704
(Xuanji Pavilion)

128
00:10:39,919 --> 00:10:40,419
News!

129
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:42,960
Go ahead.

130
00:10:43,559 --> 00:10:46,039
The people placed
around Master Chaosheng failed.

131
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:50,039
None returned?

132
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:50,720
None.

133
00:11:08,159 --> 00:11:08,960
Honey.

134
00:11:13,519 --> 00:11:15,759
You've yet to mention
the stakes of our last match.

135
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:18,519
But I do have a question to ask you.

136
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:20,080
What question?

137
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:23,080
Actually,

138
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:27,639
you know some martial arts, don't you?

139
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,879
Because you taught me well.

140
00:11:33,559 --> 00:11:36,000
Didn't you use it well yesterday?

141
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:49,240
Just a coincidence
in the heat of the moment.

142
00:11:56,799 --> 00:11:58,200
Was it really a coincidence?

143
00:11:58,639 --> 00:11:59,480
What else

144
00:12:00,279 --> 00:12:01,480
would it be?

145
00:12:02,639 --> 00:12:03,480
Zhaoxi.

146
00:12:29,200 --> 00:12:30,799
Zhaoxi is truly blessed,

147
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:32,360
having such a beautiful wife.

148
00:12:32,399 --> 00:12:34,799
Even as a woman,
I still want to marry you.

149
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:36,200
You must be kidding.

150
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:41,200
But as for Zuixian Building,
I've already planned to sell it again.

151
00:12:44,759 --> 00:12:45,799
You're right.

152
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:49,240
Rather than perform upfront,
I prefer to watch behind the scenes.

153
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:54,840
But I've heard
an interesting thing recently.

154
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:59,000
Half a month ago, a man paid guards
in Zuixian Building to corner himself.

155
00:12:59,480 --> 00:13:00,679
Such a thing happened?

156
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:02,840
I find it strange too.

157
00:13:03,039 --> 00:13:07,200
But I heard that from this,
the man won the favor of a beauty.

158
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:08,799
He did achieve his wish.

159
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,440
What do you think, Yuluo?

160
00:13:14,679 --> 00:13:15,440
Die!

161
00:13:15,440 --> 00:13:16,240
Serves you right!

162
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:27,120
Don't be afraid. I'll bring you home.

163
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:35,120
Even we at the Xuanji Pavilion
haven't heard of such a thing.

164
00:13:35,399 --> 00:13:38,320
You really do see and hear everything.

165
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:41,559
I don't know as much as you do.

166
00:13:41,639 --> 00:13:44,600
But now, I'm the owner
of Zuixian Building.

167
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:47,279
And I've used some little tricks.

168
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:53,440
It's a perfect fit. You're thoughtful.

169
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:55,159
Don't forget the bridal crown.

170
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:56,279
It must be arriving soon.

171
00:14:05,559 --> 00:14:07,000
How come you're the one sending it?

172
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:10,919
I ran into it outside
and brought it in conveniently.

173
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:17,200
You chat. I won't disturb you two.

174
00:14:22,440 --> 00:14:24,960
Meeting before marriage
is said to be unlucky.

175
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:28,279
We've been married for days.
It's just a formality now.

176
00:14:29,679 --> 00:14:31,120
You need me to complete the wedding.

177
00:14:31,720 --> 00:14:34,039
What plans do you have after that?

178
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:39,919
What about you? What's your plan?

179
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:50,200
I once thought
making him the Crown Prince

180
00:14:50,679 --> 00:14:53,519
against all opposition
was protecting him.

181
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:58,720
But how many assassination attempts
did he face as a child?

182
00:15:00,879 --> 00:15:02,399
Later, I thought,

183
00:15:03,279 --> 00:15:06,320
neglect and distance
were the way to protect him.

184
00:15:06,759 --> 00:15:07,720
But the result?

185
00:15:08,600 --> 00:15:10,399
My years of neglect

186
00:15:10,399 --> 00:15:12,799
were met with the news of his death.

187
00:15:13,720 --> 00:15:15,799
That woman was already dead.

188
00:15:16,519 --> 00:15:19,039
Why would anyone still harm him?

189
00:15:20,159 --> 00:15:22,720
Your Majesty,
please take care of your health.

190
00:15:27,559 --> 00:15:30,519
Those bandits alone
wouldn't have had such nerve.

191
00:15:33,879 --> 00:15:34,919
Xuanji Pavilion.

192
00:15:36,399 --> 00:15:37,000
Yes.

193
00:15:38,039 --> 00:15:39,440
Have them investigate.

194
00:15:39,960 --> 00:15:42,200
I want to know who is behind this.

195
00:15:42,639 --> 00:15:43,679
Yes, Your Majesty.

196
00:15:50,879 --> 00:15:54,960
Babe, this time, it's up to you.

197
00:15:55,639 --> 00:15:56,919
Be good.

198
00:15:59,279 --> 00:16:02,679
My plan mustn't fail.

199
00:16:03,720 --> 00:16:05,039
Got it?

200
00:16:11,968 --> 00:16:13,760
(Heaven)

201
00:17:09,680 --> 00:17:11,519
Master, everything is settled.

202
00:17:12,039 --> 00:17:16,400
I buried the remains when you were
at Master Chaosheng's courtyard.

203
00:17:17,200 --> 00:17:20,079
Neither his men
nor the Xuanji Pavilion noticed it.

204
00:17:21,160 --> 00:17:22,119
Anything else?

205
00:17:22,759 --> 00:17:24,640
I encountered another tail.

206
00:17:25,160 --> 00:17:28,279
His martial arts are mediocre,
but his qinggong is exceptional.

207
00:17:28,480 --> 00:17:30,039
After I detected his trail,

208
00:17:30,039 --> 00:17:32,160
it took some effort to shake him off.

209
00:17:32,880 --> 00:17:36,799
He is the same person
who took the measurements last time.

210
00:18:12,720 --> 00:18:15,160
It was you? Master!

211
00:18:20,759 --> 00:18:21,640
Understood.

212
00:18:23,799 --> 00:18:24,480
Master.

213
00:18:25,359 --> 00:18:26,599
Regarding Master Chaosheng...

214
00:18:29,759 --> 00:18:30,480
Let's go.

215
00:18:45,480 --> 00:18:46,599
What are you doing here?

216
00:18:50,319 --> 00:18:51,559
Xuan Qing stays.

217
00:18:51,839 --> 00:18:53,839
You can say it right now.

218
00:18:56,559 --> 00:18:57,599
Everyone, leave.

219
00:18:58,039 --> 00:18:58,839
- Yes.
- Yes.

220
00:19:06,680 --> 00:19:08,039
Do you really mean to help me?

221
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:09,960
I will help you,

222
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:13,200
and the family business affairs
will also continue as before

223
00:19:13,680 --> 00:19:15,599
regardless of who becomes
our family head.

224
00:20:58,846 --> 00:21:03,909
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

225
00:21:04,446 --> 00:21:09,767
♪Ancient alleys guard time's secrets♪

226
00:21:10,334 --> 00:21:16,962
♪Bluestones bear life's imprints♪

227
00:21:16,962 --> 00:21:21,726
♪Falling petals, endless longing♪

228
00:21:21,726 --> 00:21:24,062
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

229
00:21:24,062 --> 00:21:30,762
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

230
00:21:30,762 --> 00:21:37,534
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

231
00:21:37,534 --> 00:21:44,670
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

232
00:21:44,670 --> 00:21:49,054
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

233
00:21:49,054 --> 00:21:51,678
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

234
00:21:51,678 --> 00:21:58,312
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

235
00:21:58,312 --> 00:22:04,862
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

236
00:22:04,862 --> 00:22:11,986
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

237
00:22:12,076 --> 00:22:16,446
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

238
00:22:16,446 --> 00:22:19,154
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

239
00:22:19,154 --> 00:22:25,054
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

240
00:22:25,694 --> 00:22:31,682
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪
